</taxonomicName>
, head. 
<emphasis id="E6F5C722060FFFFCFD59F86500EE85DC" bold="true" box="[691,710,1974,1998]" pageId="2" pageNumber="59">A</emphasis>
. head, front coxae and thorax ca. anterolateral view; 
<emphasis id="E6F5C722060FFFFCFAF4F865071885DC" bold="true" box="[1310,1328,1974,1998]" pageId="2" pageNumber="59">B</emphasis>
. antenna, medial view; 
<emphasis id="E6F5C722060FFFFCFEC2F805031385FC" bold="true" box="[296,315,2006,2030]" pageId="2" pageNumber="59">C</emphasis>
